Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.71,0:00:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.78,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.64,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.44,0:00:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.72,0:01:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.83,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.47,0:01:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开地球的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.77,0:01:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙殖民卫星的生活里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.51,0:01:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，地球圈统一联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.34,0:01:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉正义及和平为名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以压倒性的军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.58,0:01:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压制着各个殖民卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.02,0:01:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.66,0:01:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作战名称[流星作战]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.19,0:01:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和联合反目的部份卫星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决定把伪装为流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这次作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已被联合总部发觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太…太过份…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.01,0:02:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会杀死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.02,0:02:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二话\N[人称死神的钢弹]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到了，希洛同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你昨日撕烂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐的邀请卡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何要做那种事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身为同学也觉得愤怒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.88,0:02:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你身为男子汉\N不觉得羞耻的吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次起长话短说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁你还有命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.27,0:03:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才的是希洛同学!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确是他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.84,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好利害，虽然外表不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢吞吞在做什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为不是机动战士专用舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以须要时间部署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.79,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之把所有水中机动战士放落海中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.63,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长，SMS的杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有通讯来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯的宠儿有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来很棘手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你无关!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的说话...我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果工程没大进展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我恐怕那会影响联合总部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对舰长你的能力评价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乱讲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正在用新型潜水母舰航行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但引擎有问题正头痛着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别想要军队浪费无谓的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你替我们的潜水母舰修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的空母吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当作报答你，我会借给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的最新水中机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[派西斯]和[坎沙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此，你让我领功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我对故障一事守口如瓶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你意下如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，你快点上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉，这艘舰完全正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.69,0:04:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不那样说他不会同意我们协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们重视实绩多过名声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家，人到齐了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，开始上马术课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.88,0:04:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日，我们直接实习\N来谈谈如何让马原地打转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛同学呢?他不在?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他老是神出鬼没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.26,0:05:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他马术好...根本不需要上马术课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用这个就能毁灭它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深海用鱼雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够诱导追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海军的武器库吗?距离不远...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着是细部调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛的入学费未缴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住宿费未缴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学校援助金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搜查希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们明天打扰你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种无精打采的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是难得的生日吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请笑一下，莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有秘密的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多秘密，所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密被知道，所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看可怕的\N悬疑小说吗，小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.26,0:06:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果三枚这种鱼雷直接击中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就能诱导自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在它被OZ夺去前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要毁灭它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要了结一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深海5500的位置有金属反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，出动坎沙和派西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉，请让我出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙和深海的情况不同啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，请你交给我去办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派西斯出动后，坎沙跟着出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来指挥   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现海军机动战士的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个舰长发觉了\N我们的行动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆炸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.22,0:07:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在和我们相同的深度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士相继被击毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停航，查清楚情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派西斯和坎沙怎样!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，叫他们先行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟发生什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌袭!但不能确认敌人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有机动战士没有回音!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向这地点投掷爆雷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉的\N潜水母舰在那深度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管!敌人可能就是那小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰队开始了爆雷攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无能的男人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常嘈吵，发生什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.79,0:08:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心，敌人看来在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.83,0:09:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部钢弹不会还能动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.36,0:09:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会，但别大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样，被这么多爆雷击中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人一定支持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.37,0:09:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.21,0:09:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧，看见我的人全部都要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.73,0:10:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日难得大家为了我齐聚一堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜真是不胜感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.10,0:10:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生日快乐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，你真的要出去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.78,0:10:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能为了\N莉莉娜留多一会吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.29,0:10:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别介意，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.96,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你的苦衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些相片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新闻时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.41,0:11:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据军队的公布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坠落在世界五处地方的陨石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部份已经被烧毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，它们不是传闻中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民卫星的人造物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人的，希洛一定在那里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那么希洛是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,星星王子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要迟到莉莉娜小姐的派对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.19,0:11:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才的是希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.06,0:11:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ已经开始行动，赶得及吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?你想加入我们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有经验吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.22,0:12:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种东西，什么也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.23,0:12:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它不会攻击不是敌人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野兽很单纯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.85,0:12:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这男孩真古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷，饮品我拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦你，请放在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得地球怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.28,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美丽，非常，非常美丽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.33,0:13:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然…地球这么美丽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.24,0:13:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,物资搬去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.91,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放在这里就行   这种地方!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把大量物资\N交给一个小孩做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要问，我已收了货车的费用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.67,0:14:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，来，吹熄它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吹熄蜡烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.28,0:14:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像赶得及主要的项目呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生日快乐，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.78,0:14:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，希洛果然没来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，那真的是他吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看见希洛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，在海岸公路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，好可笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他正在驾驶救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是认错人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救护车?不会有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.30,0:14:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么那部救护车向哪里去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军队的港口方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，你去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.04,0:14:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家继续享受派对我马上回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去港口的话，我送你去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我们和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别跟来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她平时不会那样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你想做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要杀谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是里欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，钢弹在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.79,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事?没有其他金属反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!我用肉眼看到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，通知杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗，找到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.23,0:15:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但吓了我一跳，它完全没损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制造出难以想像的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.44,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，把它回收后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也能变成怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心海流，我们在这深度等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，准备钢爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆装置吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么光!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人!敌人呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然能在水里使用热能武器!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别看小我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢了!我赢了!杰克斯特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是OZ的新型机，真难应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.28,0:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是联合的目标吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆装置!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.89,0:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我的机体一模一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连自爆装置的位置也一样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用毁掉它啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我当备用零件机吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点!运走死伤者!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救伤队!\N你们在做什么?快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事!?\N为何没有救护队!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.33,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你在做什么?告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.07,0:19:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是鱼雷吧，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.98,0:19:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说话，希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.26,0:19:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.74,0:19:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这情形怎样看\N你也比较像坏人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没受伤吧?小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别勉强啊，因为你是伤者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和这个人有何仇怨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.78,0:20:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，我反而变成坏人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我计算错误吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.23,0:20:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，虽然好像有点内情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但立即离开这里比较好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是为了你的安全着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要来吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是我的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.25,0:21:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做什么!笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.86,0:21:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样，一切完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务完成了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙知道\N钢弹合金的破坏数值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.19,0:21:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那机动战士的驾驶员\N就是这家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.73,0:21:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这两个人是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.17,0:21:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.43,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坎沙和派西斯也没有回音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看过钢弹一眼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.78,0:22:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能从战场回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.21,0:22:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会成为不祥之物就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.70,0:22:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.70,0:22:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
